metadata.name: Lady Summer
metadata.description:
Lady Summer is of course the hottest of the four sisters. Behind her we see the summer sun giving this lady a nice tanned skin.

This digitally drawn artwork features warm green tones and a lot of details such as flowers, animals and plants.

This stunning lady comes with a commercial license that can be found here:  
https://foundation.app/@ArjenRoos/nftcl/1
